#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:2
msgid "料号封装和分组"
msgstr "Part Numbers, Packages, and Grouping"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:4
msgid ""
"本章介绍如何通过”封装 (Package) + 料号 (PN)” "
"建立结构化的元件分组与复用体系：当多个元件具有相同封装或同时共享封装+料号时，可自动归入同一分组；其检测参数、训练样本与评估结果可在组内聚合。"
msgstr ""
"This chapter shows how to build structured component grouping and reuse "
"through **Package + Part Number (PN)**: when multiple components share the "
"same package — or share both package and part number — they can be auto-"
"bucketed into one group, and their inspection parameters, training samples, "
"and evaluation results aggregate at the group level."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:7
msgid "核心概念"
msgstr "Core concepts"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:9
msgid "**封装 (Package)** ：几何/焊盘布局形态。是分组的第一层级（顶层）。"
msgstr ""
"**Package**: the geometric / pad-layout form factor. The top-level grouping "
"key."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:10
msgid "**料号 (PN)** ：同一封装下的具体物料型号（可包含品牌/规格差异）。"
msgstr ""
"**Part Number (PN)**: a specific part variant within a package (covering "
"vendor or spec differences)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:11
msgid "**分组 (Grouping)** ：系统按照”封装 → 料号 → 单个元件”建立层级，支持按料号、封装、单个元件进行查看。"
msgstr ""
"**Grouping**: the system organizes components into the hierarchy **Package →"
" Part Number → Component**, with views that can be switched among Part "
"Number, Package, and individual Component."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:12
msgid "**共享参数** ：同组的检测参数（如检测阈值）可一次设置，所有成员继承。"
msgstr ""
"**Shared parameters**: inspection parameters (thresholds, ratio bands, etc.)"
" can be set once at the group level; every member inherits them."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:15
msgid "添加封装与料号"
msgstr "Adding packages and part numbers"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:31
msgid "添加方式："
msgstr "There are two paths:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:21
msgid "自动编程导入 CAD："
msgstr "**Import a CAD file during Auto-Programming**:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:19
msgid "CAD 表格中含有丝印/标识、封装、料号、坐标、角度等字段。"
msgstr ""
"the CAD spreadsheet carries fields for silkscreen / designator, package, "
"part number, coordinates, and rotation angle."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:20
msgid "在自动编程向导中导入后：创建封装条目 → 关联料号 → 建立封装/料号层级 → 将元件挂接。"
msgstr ""
"after importing in the Auto-Programming wizard, the system creates package "
"entries, links them to part numbers, builds the package/PN hierarchy, and "
"attaches components."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:21
msgid "缺失字段（如料号）时会按封装先分组，可后续手动补录。"
msgstr ""
"When a field is missing (e.g. part number), components are first grouped by "
"package; fill the rest in manually later."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:31
msgid "手动添加："
msgstr "**Add manually**:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:24
msgid "在模板编辑器中，从元件列表视图下，选中一个元件，在右侧设置栏打开模板。"
msgstr ""
"In the Template Editor, switch to the Component list view, select a "
"component, and open its template in the right-hand panel."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst
msgid "组件属性填写示例"
msgstr "Example: filling in component properties"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:30
msgid "按需编辑其封装、料号字段。点击保存即可。"
msgstr "Edit the package and part-number fields as needed, then click Save."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:31
msgid "可选：将该标准化元件 **保存到私有库**，便于下次复用。或者可以从私有库的元件替换当前产品的元件（见”从库中添加”一节）。"
msgstr ""
"Optional: **Save to Private Library** so the standardized component can be "
"reused later, or replace the current product's component from a private-"
"library entry (see *Add from Library* below)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:34
msgid "启用或关闭分组参与"
msgstr "Enabling and disabling group participation"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:36
msgid "每个元件具有 **连接封装** 与 **连接料号** 两个开关（默认开启）。"
msgstr ""
"Every component carries two switches — **Link Package** and **Link Part "
"No.** — both on by default."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:42
msgid "**连接封装**：决定该元件是否加入其封装分组的统计与参数继承。"
msgstr ""
"**Link Package**: whether the component joins its package group's statistics"
" and parameter inheritance."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:43
msgid "**连接料号**：决定该元件是否参与对应料号的二级分组汇总。"
msgstr ""
"**Link Part No.**: whether the component joins the second-tier roll-up for "
"its part number."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:45
msgid "典型使用场景："
msgstr "Typical use cases:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:47
msgid "临时单独调参：可暂时关闭某个异常样本的继承，单独修改；确认后再重新加入。"
msgstr ""
"Temporary one-off tuning — turn off inheritance for an unusual sample, "
"adjust it on its own, verify, then re-link."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:48
msgid "关闭链接分组：当发现某个元件与当前分组内的元件区别较大时，如颜色不同、几何不同时，可以选择取消其链接。"
msgstr ""
"Drop a member out of the group — if a component differs substantially from "
"the rest of the group (different color, different geometry), unlink it."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:51
msgid "分组层级与视图"
msgstr "Hierarchy and views"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:53
msgid "系统层级：封装 → 料号 → 元件。"
msgstr "System hierarchy: **Package → Part Number → Component**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:55
msgid "左侧元件列表支持三种视图，通过顶部选项卡切换："
msgstr ""
"The component list on the left supports three views, switched from the tab "
"strip at the top:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:-1
msgid "元件列表视图切换示意"
msgstr "Component-list view switcher"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:61
msgid "**元件**：平铺所有单体，适合逐件核对。展开某行后，可查看该元件的各检测类型。"
msgstr ""
"**Component**: flat list of every component — best for one-by-one review. "
"Expand a row to see the component's inspection types."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:62
msgid "**料号**：列表显示所有料号，将共享同一料号且已连接的元件折叠为一组；展开后可操作组内的所有检测类型。料号未填写的元件显示为”未知料号”。"
msgstr ""
"**Part Number**: lists all part numbers; components sharing the same PN that"
" are linked collapse into one group. Expand a group to manage its inspection"
" types. Components with no PN appear under *Unknown Part Number*."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:63
msgid "**封装**：列表显示所有封装，将共享同一封装且已连接的元件折叠为一组；展开后可操作组内的所有检测类型。封装未填写的元件显示为”未知封装”。"
msgstr ""
"**Package**: lists all packages; components sharing the same package that "
"are linked collapse into one group. Expand a group to manage its inspection "
"types. Components with no package appear under *Unknown Package*."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:65
msgid "在封装/料号视图下："
msgstr "In the Package and Part Number views:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst
msgid "结果图表示例"
msgstr "Example: result chart"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:75
msgid "选中某封装或料号 → 右侧可汇总显示该组全部成员的统计（训练集数据的数量、评估结果和图表）。"
msgstr ""
"Select a package or part number and the right panel shows aggregated "
"statistics for every member — training-set counts, evaluation results, and "
"charts."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:76
msgid "训练/评估后，可切换”封装”视图查看整体质量；定位某封装异常集中度。"
msgstr ""
"After training/evaluation, switch to the **Package** view to see the overall"
" quality and pinpoint packages with concentrated NGs."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:77
msgid "进入数据集浏览时，可过滤”当前封装”快速聚焦样本一致性（如焊料外形、引脚偏移模式）。"
msgstr ""
"When browsing the dataset, filter by *current package* to quickly assess "
"sample consistency (solder shape, lead-offset pattern, and so on)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:80
msgid "从库中添加"
msgstr "Add from Library"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:82
msgid "点击元件列表上方的 **从库中添加** 按钮，打开 **查找模板** 对话框。"
msgstr ""
"Click **Add from Library** above the component list to open the **Find "
"Template** dialog."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:-1
msgid "查找模板对话框：元件库（公共 / 私有）面板、模板列表与右侧元件信息预览"
msgstr ""
"Find Template dialog: library navigator (Public / Private), template list, "
"and the component-info preview on the right."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:88
msgid "对话框左侧为 **元件库** 导航栏，包含两个折叠分区："
msgstr ""
"The left side of the dialog hosts the **Library** navigator with two "
"collapsible sections:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:90
msgid "**公共**：系统内置的封装模板，按类别浏览或搜索。"
msgstr ""
"**Public**: built-in package templates, browsable or searchable by category."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:91
msgid "**私有**：用户自行保存的模板，按封装编号列出。可通过 **私有库导出** 和 **导入私有库** 按钮备份或迁移私有库。"
msgstr ""
"**Private**: templates the user has saved, listed by package number. Use "
"**Export Private Library** and **Import Private Library** to back up or "
"migrate it."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:93
msgid "中间区域为模板搜索结果列表，列出匹配的模板条目，显示以下列："
msgstr ""
"The middle column lists matching templates with the following columns:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:95
msgid "**封装**：模板的封装编号。"
msgstr "**Package**: the template's package code."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:96
msgid "**料号**：模板的料号。"
msgstr "**Part Number**: the template's part number."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:97
msgid "**创建时间**：模板创建时间。"
msgstr "**Created**: the template's creation time."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:98
msgid "操作列：私有库模板可 **删除**；公共模板不可删除。"
msgstr ""
"Actions column: private templates can be **Deleted**; public templates "
"cannot."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:100
msgid "点击列表中某行可在右侧预览区查看 **元件信息**，包括封装、料号、描述、元件宽度（mm）和元件长度（mm），同时显示该模板的图形预览。"
msgstr ""
"Click a row to see the **Component Info** preview on the right — package, "
"part number, description, width (mm), and length (mm) — alongside a "
"graphical preview of the template."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:102
msgid "确认后点击 **使用此模板**，将模板应用到当前选中位置的元件。"
msgstr ""
"Click **Use this template** to apply the template to the currently-selected "
"component position."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:105
msgid "保存到私有库"
msgstr "Save to Private Library"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:107
msgid "在模板编辑器中完成元件的封装、料号配置后，可将其保存至私有库以供后续产品复用："
msgstr ""
"Once a component's package and part-number configuration is complete in the "
"Template Editor, you can save it to the private library for future product "
"reuse:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/part_library_and_grouping.rst:109
msgid ""
"在右侧元件属性面板中，找到 **保存到私有库** "
"按钮并点击，系统将当前元件的封装定义（包括检测区域及参数）保存为私有模板，下次可通过”从库中添加”检索并应用。"
msgstr ""
"In the component-properties panel on the right, find **Save to Private "
"Library** and click it. The current component's package definition — "
"including inspection regions and parameters — is saved as a private template"
" that can later be retrieved through **Add from Library**."

